    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int id, String title, String description, String location, int contactId, String type, DateTimeValue start, DateTimeValue end, DateTimeValue createdAt, DateTimeValue updatedAt, String createdBy, String updatedBy, int custId, int userId)
      Instantiates Appointment objects. Use contactId to fetch the contact for the appointment
      Parameters:
      id - The appointment ID.
      title - The appointment title.
      description - The appointment description.
      location - The appointment location.
      contactId - The contact associated with the Appointment
      type - The appointment type.
      start - The appointment start DateTimeValue object.
      end - The appointment end DateTimeValue object.
      createdAt - The appointment creation DateTimeValue object.
      updatedAt - The appointment recent modification DateTimeValue object.
      createdBy - The appointment author.
      updatedBy - The appointment modification author
      userId - The user ID associated with the appointment.
      custId - The customer ID associated with the appointment.
